  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even [NON-ENGLISH] was bombed the first Friday night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the third of-- I became second in command of the company, because the professional captain-- I was a new lieutenant-- captain was the officer in charge.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was his right hand, the second in command.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When we went on the [? sixth, ?] we have the first [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] attack by the German motorized army by the city of [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this what happened, that our company commander was killed, and I took over the company.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we stayed for two days defending this particular [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were about 400 meters away, and I was shooting, and I was-- I didn't see that my bullet to shoot anybody.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One things I know that my company was completely almost wiped out. 240 soldiers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I took out from under fire about 45.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's all there is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All got killed or wounded or-- or run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who knows what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was wounded day after.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was about seven-- seven of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then you went to a German [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was still limping and still-- our company was first towards the German [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] invaders.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we start to retreat, the whole division, my company was the last one protecting the retreat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were going toward the [? wolf. ?] Toward east.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And by the city of-- on River [NON-ENGLISH], we dig in, and we decide to stand up against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we were sitting there, I remember like today, this was around this 20th or 22nd of September, two tanks come from the west side, and about three tanks from the east side, the German tanks and the Russian tanks.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we start standing up.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
